g/resource/Revenge\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another trick\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"another few tricks\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[He] wanted to keep it a little safe, did not want to hurt it even more.\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2470, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did the best I could do.\\\"\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 16-year-old Brown is exactly the sort of athlete the International Olympic Committee hoped to attract when it introduced more \\\"urban\\\" sports.\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2557, \"end\": 2588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 16-year-old Brown\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly the sort\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2552}, {\"ngram\": \"more \\\"urban\\\" sports\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has more than a million Instagram followers and more than 2 million on TikTok.\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2721, \"end\": 2727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2847663218199267e-38, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than a million Instagram followers\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has her own song, her own shoe and even her own Barbie doll.\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2781, \"end\": 2787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbie\", \"score\": 0.999999999737156, \"rank\": 2.6298060415029124e-10, \"text\": \"Barbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her own song\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"her own shoe\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is young and fearless, with international appeal and a multinational hinterland, born in Japan to a Japanese mother and her British father, who inspired her to take up skateboarding, while growing up in California and representing Britain.\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 3038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2888, \"end\": 2893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9862899432720442, \"rank\": 0.009630483693917342, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 2899, \"end\": 2907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9998810779334371, \"rank\": 6.080727564758347e-05, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2923, \"end\": 2930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9992167498138571, \"rank\": 0.0007797945220854279, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3002, \"end\": 3012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9999753217278486, \"rank\": 2.1271297682291394e-05, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}, {\"begin\": 3030, \"end\": 3037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999904159731134, \"rank\": 9.531666582014167e-06, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"international appeal\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"a multinational hinterland\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Change or be changed,\\\" goes the mantra of IOC president Thomas Bach, and Brown is the epitome of his Olympic evolution.\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3082, \"end\": 3085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.44051077360919e-26, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 3096, \"end\": 3107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mantra\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3078}, {\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3118}, {\"ngram\": \"the epitome\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3133}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic evolution\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She showed her spirit here.\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3188, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her spirit\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Injuries are becoming an essential part of the Sky Brown story.\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Injuries\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3197}, {\"ngram\": \"an essential part\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3228}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sky Brown story\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She suffered a horrific crash in the build-up to Tokyo after falling from a height, and here in Paris it seemed like her race might have been run.\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3399, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3302, \"end\": 3307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.999980456380839, \"rank\": 1.9543998057837597e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 3349, \"end\": 3354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999422471, \"rank\": 5.7731025519387897e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a horrific crash\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3282}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3298}, {\"ngram\": \"a height\", \"from\": 3327, \"to\": 3335}, {\"ngram\": \"her race\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was visibly upset after her fall in qualifying but somehow regrouped and put it together in the final.\", \"from\": 3400, \"to\": 3506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her fall\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3436}, {\"ngram\": \"qualifying\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3450}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 3496, \"to\": 3505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wearing black clothes over white shoes on a sparkling white board, Brown made a middling start, scoring 80.57 in the first of her three runs in a competition of speed, height and skill in which only your best score counts.\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3730, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\":