ore of 91.60 propelled her into second place behind Hiraki.\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A score\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4000}, {\"ngram\": \"second place\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4041}, {\"ngram\": \"Hiraki\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trew went even better, scoring a giant 93.18 with her final run and pushing Brown down to third.\", \"from\": 4058, \"to\": 4154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Trew\", \"from\": 4058, \"to\": 4062}, {\"ngram\": \"a giant\", \"from\": 4089, \"to\": 4096}, {\"ngram\": \"her final run\", \"from\": 4108, \"to\": 4121}, {\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \"from\": 4134, \"to\": 4139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She took one final pep talk from her dad - \\\"the score does not matter, suck it in and enjoy it\\\" - and then she launched, performing the same routine with an added injection of speed that helped her to fit in one more trick at the finish.\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4392, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one final pep talk\", \"from\": 4164, \"to\": 4182}, {\"ngram\": \"her dad\", \"from\": 4188, \"to\": 4195}, {\"ngram\": \"the score\", \"from\": 4199, \"to\": 4208}, {\"ngram\": \"the same routine\", \"from\": 4287, \"to\": 4303}, {\"ngram\": \"an added injection\", \"from\": 4309, \"to\": 4327}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 4331, \"to\": 4336}, {\"ngram\": \"one more trick\", \"from\": 4363, \"to\": 4377}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish\", \"from\": 4381, \"to\": 4391}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the buzzer went, she leapt out of the bowl and collapsed in an exhausted heap.\", \"from\": 4393, \"to\": 4476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the buzzer\", \"from\": 4398, \"to\": 4408}, {\"ngram\": \"the bowl\", \"from\": 4432, \"to\": 4440}, {\"ngram\": \"an exhausted heap\", \"from\": 4458, \"to\": 4475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her score of 92.32 lifted her above Hiraki for silver, but the Japanese skater still had on